OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: George
OL,4,CChandler
OL,6,FGeorge Chandler, Age: 98, Royal Navy
OL,8,FInterviewed 5 March 2024
OL,10,FA crewman on a British motor torpedo
OL,11,Fboat leaving from Newhaven, George
OL,12,FChandler from Burgess Hill crossed the
OL,13,FChannel on the afternoon of D-Day.
OL,15,FHis vessel was an armed guard for the
OL,16,FAmerican Rangers heading to Omaha and
OL,17,FUtah.
