OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: George
OL,4,CChandler
OL,6,F"We laid off and we could see these
OL,7,Fyoung Rangers.
OL,9,F"Some were younger than me and I was
OL,10,F19 at the time. We watched them come
OL,11,Fin and get slaughtered. They weren't
OL,12,Fkilled, they were slaughtered. They
OL,13,Fdidn't stand a chance.
OL,15,F"We could see them through these big
OL,16,Fsubmarine night glasses we had.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
