OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: George
OL,4,CChandler
OL,6,F"Some of them were killed before they
OL,7,Feven got off their boats and assault
OL,8,Fcraft, and I wouldn't ask any mother's
OL,9,Fson to go through what they went
OL,10,Fthrough.
OL,12,F"Like all these things, when you go to
OL,13,Fa memorial you are there again on the
OL,14,Fspot.
OL,16,F"While I am talking to you I am re-
OL,17,Fliving that. I can see these
OL,18,Fyoungsters being mown down as they
OL,19,Ftried to land.
