OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: George
OL,4,CChandler
OL,6,F"They must have been the bloodiest
OL,7,Fbeaches of the whole of D-Day."
OL,9,FThe Americans finally secured a
OL,10,Ffoothold and Mr Chandler's ship
OL,11,Freturned to Newhaven. It then spent
OL,12,Fseveral months carrying out patrols of
OL,13,Fthe French coast.
